{"tid":2258021,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[超突發］白羅斯再次大規模示威 要求總理今晚12點辭職 否則全國罷工 俄狗出埋閃光彈！","createTime":"2020-10-25T16:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T07:31:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"56a6479d778038073288f30fc147d591df8c63a4","tid":2258021,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/reuters/status/1320398473963982850?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Freuters%2Fstatus%2F1320398473963982850%3Fs%3D21&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=b3406918\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Freuters%2Fstatus%2F1320398473963982850%3Fs%3D21&h=916b8124\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/reuters/status/1320398473963982850?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nBelarus police fire stun grenades at protesters as opposition threatens national strike<br />\n<br />\n(Reuters) - Belarusian police used stun grenades against protesters on Sunday as tens of thousands of people headed towards Independence Palace in the capital Minsk demanding that President Alexander Lukashenko resign.<br />\n<br />\nProtesters carrying the red-and-white flags of the Belarusian opposition movement scattered as loud bangs and flashes lit up the city's streets after nightfall, videos showed.<br />\n<br />\nThe police action came hours before the expiration of an ultimatum set by the opposition: Lukashenko must resign by midnight or face a national strike."},{"pid":"af59c9d77ab3f13674dd0857a34f9e5dc2678a25","tid":2258021,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T16:26:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/bfreetheatre/status/1320392773611159552?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbfreetheatre%2Fstatus%2F1320392773611159552%3Fs%3D21&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=ce1e7e4b\" data-ef-url